summary: 3 New spells added to your elder scrolls game
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds three new spells to your game. What is so special about these spells? They pretty much  Unrelenting Force plus a fire, ice, or shock spell. 

The spells are called:

Sparks of Resistance
Flames of Resistance
Frost of Resistance

Want to add the spell or its tome through the console? Type \"help Resistance 0\" (without the quotes) in the console to get its code then use \"player.addspell\" or \"player.additem\" to add it
author: themusician6
